'''雷內·亞歷山大·「亞歷克斯」·阿科斯塔'''（{{lang-en|Rene Alexander "Alex" Acosta}}；{{bd|1969年|1月16日|}}）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://archive.tcpalm.com/news/us-attorney-alexander-acosta-to-lead-fius-law-school-ep-398936799-347426931.html |title=U.S. Attorney Alexander Acosta to lead FIU's law school |last1=Weaver |first1=Jay |last2=Yanez |first2=Luisa |date=2009-05-28 |work=[[The_Miami_Herald|The Miami Herald]] |accessdate=2017-02-17 |archive-date=2017-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825110530/http://archive.tcpalm.com/news/us-attorney-alexander-acosta-to-lead-fius-law-school-ep-398936799-347426931.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，是[[美国|美国]]的檢察官，現任{{le|佛羅里達國際大學法學院|Florida International University College of Law}}院長。他是一名[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]人，於前總統[[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]時期被任命為[[国家劳动关系委员会|国家劳动关系委员会]]委員，其後在{{le|美國司法部民權司|United States Department of Justice Civil Rights Division|司法部民權司}}和{{le|佛羅里達州南區聯邦檢察官|United States Attorney for the Southern District of Florida|佛羅里達州南區}}{{le|美國檢察官|United States Attorney|聯邦檢察部門}}任職。期間，發生[[杰弗里·愛潑斯坦|杰弗里·愛潑斯坦]]性侵少女案。擔任檢察官的阿科斯塔在原告不知情的情况下与愛潑斯坦就性侵少女等相关指控达成[[認罪協商|認罪協商]]。双方签署的认罪协议令爱泼斯坦得以避免联邦起诉和可能面临的终身监禁，仅以较轻罪名服刑13个月，愛潑斯坦更是获准每周离开监狱6天到自己的办公室工作<ref name="xin">{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-07/13/c_1124747508.htm |title=美国劳工部长因爱泼斯坦性犯罪案辞职 |accessdate=2019-07-13 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808200459/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-07/13/c_1124747508.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年2月16日，美國總統[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]提名阿科斯塔出任[[美国劳工部长|美国劳工部长]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2017/02/trump-to-announce-alexander-acosta-as-labor-secretary-nominee-235089|title=Trump to name Alexander Acosta as labor secretary nominee|publisher=|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114054518/https://www.politico.com/story/2017/02/trump-to-announce-alexander-acosta-as-labor-secretary-nominee-235089|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/02/16/politics/donald-trump-white-house-announcement/index.html|title=Trump to announce Alexander Acosta as labor secretary pick|first=John King, Manu Raju and Dan Merica|last=CNN|publisher=|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208232429/https://www.cnn.com/2017/02/16/politics/donald-trump-white-house-announcement/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2017/02/16/president-trump-hold-press-conference/97992390/|title=Trump to name Alexander Acosta as new Labor secretary nominee|publisher=|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2020-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225061841/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2017/02/16/president-trump-hold-press-conference/97992390/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年7月，杰弗里·愛潑斯坦再度因為涉及未成年人性交易而被逮捕。阿科斯塔因对愛潑斯坦當初過於宽大处理面临舆论的巨大压力。2019年7月12日，阿科斯塔宣佈辭職<ref name="xin"/>。

